$\blueD{\angle a}$, $\greenD{\angle {b}}$ and ${\angle {CAD}}$ add up to $180\degree$.

$\begin{align}
\blueD{\angle a}+\greenD{\angle {b}}+{\angle {CAD}}&=180\degree\\\\
\blueD{\angle a}+\greenD{80\degree}+{35\degree}&=180\degree\\\\
\blueD{\angle {a}}&=\blueD{65\degree}
\end{align}$
